ìóŸRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2024-05-25-twin0248.mdŸ@e95ab06955b1163cd7567c7fa57a5e5457321318b19b2f6ad1ca14c4cfbb1174πThis week in Nushell #248ëßNushell⁄
ÿYizhePKU 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12921] rewrote 
``run_external.rs``
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12922] removed 
``std::env::set_current_dir()``
 call from 
``EngineState::merge_env()``
.
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12959] allowed byte streams with unknown type to be compatible with binary
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12955] stopped propagating glob creation error for external args
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12947] used 
``cwd``
 in 
``grid``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12939] removed list support in 
``with-env``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12909] took owned 
``Read``
 and 
``Write``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12903] made 
``get_full_help``
 take 
``&dyn Command``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12901] cleared environment for child 
``Command``
s
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12889] removed the dataframes crate and feature
.
devyn 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12949] made 
``from json --objects``
 streaming
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12919] updated mimalloc to 0.1.42
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12918] implemented streaming I/O for CSV and TSV commands
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12897] added string/binary type color to 
``ByteStream``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12892] added support for the 
``ps``
 command on FreeBSD, NetBSD, and OpenBSD
.
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12967] made the polars plugin use mimalloc
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12913] added 
``math min``
 and 
``math max``
 to the 
``bench``
 command
.
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12943] fixed 
``std help``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12908] added some completion tests
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12894] fixed range semantic in detect_columns, str substring, str index-of
.
rgwood did a bunch of refactoring+simplification for 
``explore``
: 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12940] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12920] 2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12915] 3
.
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12937] fixed a wrong column name
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12930] made small improvements to 
``debug profile``
.
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12929] added a completer for std help
.
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/12917] removed unused dependencies
.
